iterations.yara_rule:
rule Bypass_Sample
{
    meta:
        description = "Evasion bypass patterns targeting exit process detection"
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 8B EC ?? ?? ?? ?? FF 75 08 } // Skipping TEST EAX and JZX to bypass check
        $pattern1 = { 6A 5A 8B CE E8 ?? ?? ?? ?? ?? ?? ?? ?? FF 75 08 } // Skipping conditional jump offset
        $pattern2 = { ?? ?? 8B EC E8 ?? ?? ?? ?? ?? ?? ?? ?? FF 75 08 } // Skipping stack manipulation and call
    condition:
        any of them
}
